  <script>
    let total = 0;
    let cart = [];

    function addToCart(item, price) {
      total += price;
      cart.push({ item, price });
      document.getElementById("totalDisplay").innerText = `Ukupno: ${total} RSD`;
      updateReceipt();
    }

    function addNewProduct() {
      const name = document.getElementById("newProductName").value;
      const price = parseInt(document.getElementById("newProductPrice").value);
      if (name && !isNaN(price)) {
        const button = document.createElement("button");
        button.innerText = `${name} - ${price} RSD`;
        button.onclick = () => addToCart(name, price);
        document.getElementById("productButtons").appendChild(button);
        document.getElementById("newProductName").value = "";
        document.getElementById("newProductPrice").value = "";
      }
    }

    function updateReceipt() {
      let receiptItems = document.getElementById("receiptItems");
      let html = "";
      cart.forEach((entry) => {
        html += `${entry.item} - ${entry.price} RSD<br>`;
      });
      document.getElementById("receiptItems").innerHTML = html;
      document.getElementById("receiptTotal").innerText = total;
    }

    function calculateChange(method) {
      const moneyGiven = parseInt(document.getElementById("moneyGiven").value);
      let change = 0;
      if (method === "cash") {
        change = moneyGiven - total;
        document.getElementById("receiptChange").innerText =
          change >= 0 ? change : "Nema dovoljno novca";
      } else {
        document.getElementById("receiptChange").innerText = "0 (Kartica)";
      }
      document.getElementById("paymentType").innerText =
        method === "cash" ? "Gotovina" : "Kartica";
      printReceipt();
    }

    function printReceipt() {
      const content = document.getElementById("receipt").innerHTML;
      const printWindow = window.open("", "", "width=400,height=600");
      printWindow.document.write("<html><head><title>Račun</title></head><body>");
      printWindow.document.write(content);
      printWindow.document.write("</body></html>");
      printWindow.document.close();
      printWindow.print();
    }

    function resetAll() {
      total = 0;
      cart = [];
      document.getElementById("totalDisplay").innerText = `Ukupno: 0 RSD`;
      document.getElementById("moneyGiven").value = "";
      document.getElementById("receiptItems").innerHTML = "";
      document.getElementById("receiptTotal").innerText = "0";
      document.getElementById("receiptChange").innerText = "0";
      document.getElementById("paymentType").innerText = "N/A";
    }

    // Enter za naplatu karticom
    document.addEventListener("keydown", function (event) {
      if (event.key === "Enter") {
        calculateChange("card");
      }
    });
  </script>

Ako imaš Git instaliran na računaru:

  • Otvori terminal ili komandnu liniju.

  • Ukucaj:

bash
git clone https://github.com/tvojusername/ime-repozitorijuma.git

  • Time preuzimaš celu kopiju repozitorijuma.

Ako ti treba, mogu ti pomoći da odradiš neki od ovih koraka ili napravim ZIP paket od koda koji smo pravili. Samo reci!

<div id="receiptItems"></div>

<script>
let total = 0;
let cart = [];

function addToCart(item, price) {
total += price;
cart.push({ item, price });
document.getElementById("totalDisplay").innerText = `Ukupno: ${total} RSD`;
updateReceipt();
}

function addNewProduct() {
const name = document.getElementById("newProductName").value;
const price = parseInt(document.getElementById("newProductPrice").value);
if (name && !isNaN(price)) {
const button = document.createElement("button");
button.innerText = `${name} - ${price} RSD`;
button.onclick = () => addToCart(name, price);
document.getElementById("productButtons").appendChild(button);
document.getElementById("newProductName").value = "";
document.getElementById("newProductPrice").value = "";
}
}

function updateReceipt() {
let receiptItems = document.getElementById("receiptItems");
let html = "";
cart.forEach(entry => {
html += `${entry.item} - ${entry.price} RSD<br>`;
});
document.getElementById("receiptItems").innerHTML = html;
document.getElementById("receiptTotal").innerText = total;
}

function calculateChange(method) {
const moneyGiven = parseInt(document.getElementById("moneyGiven").value);
let change = 0;
if (method === 'cash') {
change = moneyGiven - total;
document.getElementById("receiptChange").innerText = change >= 0 ? change : "Nema dovoljno novca";
} else {
document.getElementById("receiptChange").innerText = "0 (Kartica)";
}
document.getElementById("paymentType").innerText = method === 'cash' ? 'Gotovina' : 'Kartica';
printReceipt();
}

function printReceipt() {
const content = document.getElementById("receipt").innerHTML;
const printWindow = window.open('', '', 'width=400,height=600');
printWindow.document.write('<html><head><title>Račun</title></head><body>');
printWindow.document.write(content);
printWindow.document.write('</body></html>');
printWindow.document.close();
printWindow.print();
}

function resetAll() {
total = 0;
cart = [];
document.getElementById("totalDisplay").innerText = `Ukupno: 0 RSD`;
document.getElementById("moneyGiven").value = "";
document.getElementById("receiptItems").innerHTML = "";
document.getElementById("receiptTotal").innerText = "0";
document.getElementById("receiptChange").innerText = "0";
document.getElementById("paymentType").innerText = "N/A";
}

// Enter za naplatu karticom
document.addEventListener("keydown", function(event) {
if (event.key === "Enter") {
calculateChange("card");
}
});
</script>
</body>
</html>
